---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Paint and Pour Pottery Candle"
  description="Combine pottery painting with candle making in one creative experience. Double the art, double the fun in Centerville, TN."
  price="$30-40 per person"
  duration="2-2.5 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="paint and pour, pottery candle, art combo, creative activities"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Paint and Pour Pottery Candle - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>
      Combine the joy of pottery painting with the satisfaction of candle making in our Paint and Pour experience. Create two beautiful pieces in one creative session that you'll treasure for years to come.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      You'll paint a pre-made pottery piece with vibrant colors, then transition to pouring your own hand-made candle with custom fragrance and color. It's two complete creative experiences in one session!
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pre-made pottery piece selection</li>
      <li>All painting supplies and paints</li>
      <li>Premium soy wax for candle making</li>
      <li>40+ fragrance options</li>
      <li>Beautiful container selection</li>
      <li>Professional pouring guidance</li>
      <li>Take-home finished candles</li>
      <li>Pottery professionally glazed and fired</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <p>
      Anyone who loves creative activities! Perfect for creative souls, art enthusiasts, couples seeking a unique date, and groups wanting extended creative time together.
    </p>

    <h3>Session Timeline</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and project overview (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Pottery piece selection (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Painting your pottery piece (40 minutes)</li>
      <li>Transition and candle selection (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Pouring your custom candle (45 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing and wrapping (10 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $30-40 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2-2.5 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 1-6 people<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your paint and pour experience!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Loved getting to do two art forms in one session! The variety kept it interesting and fun the whole time!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Alex M.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Perfect date activity! We had so much fun creating together. Pottery and candle making—best date ever!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Ryan & Tanya</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"The instructors made it so easy and fun. Left with two beautiful pieces I made myself!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Courtney W.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Pottery and Candle Combo Session</h3>
        <p>Experience both pottery and candle making in one creative session.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/pottery-and-candle-combo-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Family Pottery Painting Experience</h3>
        <p>Multi-generational creative fun with pottery painting for the whole family.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/family-pottery-painting-experience" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Pour Your Own Candle Class</h3>
        <p>Create beautiful hand-poured candles with custom colors and scents.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/pour-your-own-candle-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
